embers\" },\n 24 |   { id: \"medium\", label: \"Mid-Market Growth\", desc: \"Regional enterprise coverage, cross-system compliance pipelines.\", range: \"100 - 999 Members\" },\n 25 |   { id: \"enterprise\", label: \"Enterprise Scale\", desc: \"Global multi-region infrastructure, advanced compliance boundaries.\", range: \"1,000 - 9,999 Members\" },\n 26 |   { id: \"global-conglomerate\", label: \"Global Conglomerate\", desc: \"Air-gapped security enclaves, multi-tenant network partitioning.\", range: \"10,000+ Members\" }\n 27 | ];\n 28 | \n 29 | const CHALLENGES = [\n 30 |   { id: \"data-fragmentation\", label: \"Data Fragmentation\", icon: \"🗄️\", desc: \"Metrics trapped inside unindexed legacy silos blocking AI access.\" },\n 31 |   { id: \"compliance-risk\", label: \"Compliance & Leakage Risk\", icon: \"🔒\", desc: \"External SaaS telemetry leaks private IP. Mandates single-tenant isolated enclaves.\" },\n 32 |   { id: \"operational-latency\", label: \"Operational Loop Latency\", icon: \"⏳\", desc: \"Manual document routing, verification steps, and reporting slowing down cycles.\" },\n 33 |   { id: \"cost-explosion\", label: \"API & SaaS Cost Explosion\", icon: \"📈\", desc: \"Skyrocketing token consumption fees, unstructured billing, and overlapping tooling.\" },\n 34 |   { id: \"other\", label: \"Custom Strategic Obstacle\", icon: \"⚙️\", desc: \"Provide a custom corporate obstacle or technical constraint to resolve.\" }\n 35 | ];\n 36 | \n 37 | const OUTCOMES = [\n 38 |   { id: \"zero-retention\", label: \"Zero Retention VPC\", desc: \"Absolute secure pipelines with zero memory logging boundaries.\" },\n 39 |   { id: \"sub-150ms-latency\", label: \"Sub-150ms Execution\", desc: \"Dynamic cognitive agents performing sub-second decision loops.\" },\n 40 |   { id: \"cost-reclamation\", label: \"30%+ Expense Reclamation\", desc: \"Replace fragile external APIs with highly optimized local open models.\" },\n 41 |   { id: \"telemetry-audit\", label: \"Real-Time Telemetry Audit\", desc: \"Continuous, automatic compliance validation ledger tracks all queries.\" },\n 42 |   { id: \"fleet-orchestration\", label: \"Multi-Agent Fleet Orchestration\", desc: \"Deploy interconnected cognitive nodes working across corporate layers.\" }\n 43 | ];\n 44 | \n 45 | const TIMELINES = [\n 46 |   { id: \"30-days\", label: \"30-Day Sandbox Pilot\", desc: \"High-speed validation, limited sandbox scope, co-innovation sprint.\", weeks: 4 },\n 47 |   { id: \"90-days\", label: \"90-Day Production SOW\", desc: \"Full-scale core deployment, VPC isolation, primary systems integration.\", weeks: 12 },\n 48 |   { id: \"180-days\", label: \"180-Day Federated Rollout\", desc: \"Multi-department rollout, custom fine-tuning, cross-region peering.\", weeks: 24 },\n 49 |   { id: \"continuous\", label: \"Continuous SLA Co-Run\", desc: \"Persistent system optimization, regular compliance updates, proactive tuning.\", weeks: 52 }\n 50 | ];\n 51 | \n 52 | const ENGAGEMENT_PATHS = [\n 53 |   {\n 54 |     id: \"garage\" as const,\n 55 |     label: \"GFF Garage\",\n 56 |     badge: \"Co-Innovation Sprint\",\n 57 |     desc: \"Rapid discovery, sandboxed design, and validation proof-of-concept. Perfect for high-speed strategic alignment.\",\n 58 |     weeks: \"2 - 4 Weeks\",\n 59 |     squad: \"1 Architect, 1 Engineer\",\n 60 |     outcome: \"Validated Interactive Prototype & Baseline Architecture Blueprint\",\n 61 |     accent: \"#009DFF\"\n 62 |   },\n 63 |   {\n 64 |     id: \"foundry\" as const,\n 65 |     label: \"GFF Foundry\",\n 66 |     badge: \"Bespoke Platform Build\",\n 67 |     desc: \"Custom engineering, model optimization, and private VPC deployment. The standard choice for secure systems construction.\",\n 68 |     weeks: \"6 - 12 Weeks\",\n 69 |     squad: \"1 Lead Architect, 2 Systems Engineers, 1 Security Specialist\",\n 70 |     outcome: \"Hardened Single-Tenant Platform deployed inside private cloud\",\n 71 |     accent: \"#00FF9D\"\n 72 |   },\n 73 |   {\n 74 |     id: \"factory\" as const,\n 75 |     label: \"GFF Factory\",\n 76 |     badge: \"Industrial Scale Fleets\",\n 77 |     desc: \"High-volume cognitive agent orchestration, automated pipelines, and enterprise-wide federated data mesh networks.\",\n 78 |     weeks: \"12 - 24 Weeks\",\n 79 |     squad: \"2 Architects, 4 Core Engineers, 1 QA Auditor, 1 Delivery Director\",\n 80 |     outcome: \"Multi-agent automated workforce operating across production databases\",\n 81 |     accent: \"#9D00FF\"\n 82 |   },\n 83 |   {\n 84 |     id: \"operate\" as const,\n 85 |     label: \"GFF Operate\",\n 86 |     badge: \"SLA-Driven Co-Run\",\n 87 |     desc: \"Continuous proactive monitoring, scheduled compliance updates, model weight updates, and guaranteed performance SLAs.\",\n 88 |     weeks: \"Ongoing Execution\",\n 89 |     squad: \"Dedicated Site Reliability Fleet, Lead AI Performance Engineer\",\n 90 |     outcome: \"Guaranteed 99.9% uptime, compliance reports, and proactive optimizations\",\n 91 |     accent: \"#E5A93C\"\n 92 |   }\n 93 | ];\n 94 | \n 95 | const BUDGET_RANGES = [\n 96 |   { id: \"tier-1\", label: \"Discovery Capital ($50K - $250K)\", desc: \"Suited for GFF Garage exploration and sandbox verification.\" },\n 97 |   { id: \"tier-2\", label: \"Strategic Platform ($250K - $1M)\", desc: \"Optimal for core GFF Foundry setup and VPC deployments.\" },\n 98 |   { id: \"tier-3\", label: \"Industrial Scale ($1M+)\", desc: \"Required for GFF Factory federated rollouts and persistent co-run.\" }\n 99 | ];\n100 | \n101 | // ==========================================\n102 | // 2. Types & Interface\n103 | // ==========================================\n104 | \n105 | interface ProposalIntakeInputs {\n106 |   companyName: string;\n107 |   industry: Industry;\n108 |   companySize: CompanySize;\n109 |   primaryChallenge: string;\n110 |   customChallenge: string;\n111 |   priorityOutcomes: string[];\n112 |   targetTimeline: string;\n113 |   preferredEngagementPath: \"garage\" | \"foundry\" | \"factory\" | \"operate\";\n114 |   budgetRange: string;\n115 |   geography: string;\n116 |   stakeholders: string;\n117 | }\n118 | \n119 | const INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS: ProposalIntakeInputs = {\n120 |   companyName: \"\",\n121 |   industry: \"banking\",\n122 |   companySize: \"enterprise\",\n123 |   primaryChallenge: \"compliance-risk\",\n124 |   customChallenge: \"\",\n125 |   priorityOutcomes: [\"zero-retention\", \"sub-150ms-latency\"],\n126 |   targetTimeline: \"90-days\",\n127 |   preferredEngagementPath: \"foundry\",\n128 |   budgetRange: \"tier-2\",\n129 |   geography: \"\",\n130 |   stakeholders: \"\"\n131 | };\n132 | \n133 | const compilingMessages = [\n134 |   \"Spinning up local compiler sandbox...\",\n135 |   \"Querying GFF strategic taxonomy parameters...\",\n136 |   \"Applying regulatory compliance standards override...\",\n137 |   \"Sizing GFF delivery squad parameters...\",\n138 |   \"Configuring isolated virtual boundary rules...\",\n139 |   \"Enforcing strict zero-data retention pipelines...\",\n140 |   \"Generating premium SOW specifications...\"\n141 | ];\n142 | \n143 | export default function ProposalBuilderPage() {\n144 |   const [inputs, setInputs] = useState<ProposalIntakeInputs>(INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS);\n145 |   const [step, setStep] = useState<\"configure\" | \"compiling\" | \"preview\">(\"configure\");\n146 |   const [activeStepGate, setActiveStepGate] = useState<1 | 2 | 3>(1);\n147 |   const [compilingStepIndex, setCompilingStepIndex] = useState(0);\n148 |   const [copied, setCopied] = useState(false);\n149 |   const [saved, setSaved] = useState(false);\n150 |   const [hasSavedDraft, setHasSavedDraft] = useState(false);\n151 |   const [activePreviewSection, setActivePreviewSection] = useState<string>(\"executive-summary\");\n152 |   const [signName, setSignName] = useState(\"\");\n153 |   const [signTitle, setSignTitle] = useState(\"\");\n154 |   const [isSigned, setIsSigned] = useState(false);\n155 |   const [mounted, setMounted] = useState(false);\n156 |   const [validationErrors, setValidationErrors] = useState<Record<string, string>>({});\n157 |   const [exportToast, setExportToast] = useState<string | null>(null);\n158 |   const [isFlushing, setIsFlushing] = useState(false);\n159 | \n160 |   const handleExportClick = (type: string) => {\n161 |     setExportToast(`Premium Feature Sandbox: Exporting as ${type} requires a GFF Enterprise Control Center gateway cloud connection. This offline terminal runs in strict zero-retention memory isolation.`);\n162 |     setTimeout(() => setExportToast(null), 6000);\n163 |   };\n164 | \n165 |   useEffect(() => {\n166 |     setMounted(true);\n167 |     const draft = getToolState(\"proposal\");\n168 |     if (draft) {\n169 |       setHasSavedDraft(true);\n170 |     }\n171 |   }, []);\n172 | \n173 |   // Auto-save on input changes\n174 |   useEffect(() => {\n175 |     if (mounted) {\n176 |       saveToolState(\"proposal\", inputs);\n177 |     }\n178 |   }, [inputs, mounted]);\n179 | \n180 |   const validateStep = (gate: 1 | 2 | 3): boolean => {\n181 |     const errors: Record<string, string> = {};\n182 |     if (gate === 1) {\n183 |       if (!inputs.industry) errors.industry = \"Please select a primary industry vertical.\";\n184 |       if (!inputs.companySize) errors.companySize = \"Please specify company scale.\";\n185 |     } else if (gate === 2) {\n186 |       if (!inputs.primaryChallenge) errors.primaryChallenge = \"Please identify your primary business challenge.\";\n187 |       if (inputs.primaryChallenge === \"other\" && !inputs.customChallenge.trim()) {\n188 |         errors.customChallenge = \"Please specify your custom corporate obstacle.\";\n189 |       }\n190 |       if (inputs.priorityOutcomes.length === 0) {\n191 |         errors.priorityOutcomes = \"Please select at least one priority target outcome.\";\n192 |       }\n193 |       if (!inputs.targetTimeline) errors.targetTimeline = \"Please select a target timeline.\";\n194 |     } else if (gate === 3) {\n195 |       if (!inputs.preferredEngagementPath) errors.preferredEngagementPath = \"Please select an engagement pathway.\";\n196 |     }\n197 | \n198 |     setValidationErrors(errors);\n199 |     return Object.keys(errors).length === 0;\n200 |   };\n201 | \n202 |   const handleNextGate = () => {\n203 |     if (validateStep(activeStepGate)) {\n204 |       setActiveStepGate((prev) => (prev + 1) as 1 | 2 | 3);\n205 |     }\n206 |   };\n207 | \n208 |   const handleCompile = () => {\n209 |     if (!validateStep(3)) return;\n210 |     setStep(\"compiling\");\n211 |     setCompilingStepIndex(0);\n212 |   };\n213 | \n214 |   useEffect(() => {\n215 |     if (step !== \"compiling\") return;\n216 |     const interval = setInterval(() => {\n217 |       setCompilingStepIndex((prev) => {\n218 |         if (prev < compilingMessages.length - 1) return prev + 1;\n219 |         clearInterval(interval);\n220 |         setStep(\"preview\");\n221 |         return prev;\n222 |       });\n223 |     }, 450);\n224 |     return () => clearInterval(interval);\n225 |   }, [step]);\n226 | \n227 |   const handleSaveDraft = () => {\n228 |     saveToolState(\"proposal\", inputs);\n229 |     setSaved(true);\n230 |     setHasSavedDraft(false); // No need to prompt to restore if we just explicitly saved/synced\n231 |     setTimeout(() => setSaved(false), 2000);\n232 |   };\n233 | \n234 |   const handleRestoreDraft = () => {\n235 |     const draft = getToolState(\"proposal\");\n236 |     if (draft) {\n237 |       setInputs(draft as any);\n238 |       setHasSavedDraft(false);\n239 |     }\n240 |   };\n241 | \n242 |   const handleReset = () => {\n243 |     setIsFlushing(true);\n244 |     setTimeout(() => {\n245 |       setInputs(INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS);\n246 |       setStep(\"configure\");\n247 |       setActiveStepGate(1);\n248 |       setIsSigned(false);\n249 |       setSignName(\"\");\n250 |       setSignTitle(\"\");\n251 |       setValidationErrors({});\n252 |       clearToolState(\"proposal\");\n253 |       setHasSavedDraft(false);\n254 |       setIsFlushing(false);\n255 |     }, 450);\n256 |   };\n257 | \n258 |   const handlePrint = () => {\n259 |     if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") window.print();\n260 |   };\n261 | \n262 |   const handleCopyOutline = () => {\n263 |     const data = generateProposalData();\n264 |     const p1 = data.p1;\n265 |     const p2 = data.p2;\n266 |     const p3 = data.p3;\n267 |     const weeks = data.weeks;\n268 | \n269 |     const outlineText = `GFF AI SOVEREIGN INTEGRATION PROPOSAL & OUTLINE (FRONTEND PREVIEW ONLY)\n270 | ======================================================================\n271 | CLIENT: ${data.org} | VERTICAL: ${data.industryLabel}\n272 | OPERATIONAL SCALE: ${data.companySizeLabel} (${data.companySizeRange})\n273 | VPC DEPLOYMENT REGION: ${data.geographyLabel}\n274 | PREFERRED ENGAGEMENT PATHWAY: ${data.engagementPathObj.label} (${data.engagementPathObj.badge})\n275 | CALCULATED SOW TIMELINE: ${weeks} Weeks | BUDGET: ${data.budgetLabel}\n276 | STAKEHOLDER SPONSORS: ${data.stakeholdersLabel}\n277 | \n278 | SECTION I: EXECUTIVE SUMMARY\n279 | GFF AI recommends deploying a dedicated ${data.engagementPathObj.label} framework inside the single-tenant VPC perimeter for ${data.org} to address strategic bottlenecks in the ${data.industryLabel} sector. Over ${weeks} Weeks, GFF establishes isolated secure pipelines, delivering sovereign capabilities like ${data.selectedOutcomeLabels.join(\", \")}.\n280 | \n281 | SECTION II: CHALLENGE STATEMENT\n282 | Third-party cloud-hosted AI APIs introduce severe compliance risks and telemetry leaks. The core technical bottleneck to resolve for ${data.org} is \"${data.challengeLabel}\". Left unmitigated, data fragmentation and cost explosion will slow down operational cycles.\n283 | \n284 | SECTION III: RECOMMENDED GFF PATH\n285 | We recommend the ${data.engagementPathObj.label} path (${data.engagementPathObj.badge}) deployed completely isolated on single-tenant architecture within ${data.geographyLabel} with a strict zero data-retention layer.\n286 | \n287 | SECTION IV: PROPOSED WORKSTREAMS\n288 | - Workstream A: Hardened Perimeter Setup (Weeks 1 - ${p1}): Configure VPC boundaries and verify zero-retention.\n289 | - Workstream B: Pipeline Core Integration (Weeks ${p1 + 1} - ${p1 + p2}): Deploy OmniMesh read-only connectors and metadata layers.\n290 | - Workstream C: Agent Orchestration & Tuning (Weeks ${p1 + p2 + 1} - ${p1 + p2 + p3}): Standardize agent configurations and workflow guardrails.\n291 | - Workstream D: Telemetry Logging & Handoff (Weeks ${p1 + p2 + p3 + 1} - ${weeks}): Integrate real-time audit ledgers and operator dashboards.\n292 | \n293 | SECTION V: 90-DAY ROADMAP\n294 | - Day 1-30: Perimeter Isolation: Connect legacy data silos via OmniMesh read-only boundaries.\n295 | - Day 31-60: Agent Workflow Design: Orchestrate multi-agent decision nodes and feedback loops.\n296 | - Day 61-90: Go-Live & Certification: Scale the agent fleet and complete sovereign compliance certification.\n297 | \n298 | SECTION VI: SUGGESTED SQUAD\n299 | Squad cohort: ${data.engagementPathObj.squad}\n300 | - Lead Solutions Architect (VPC & data boundary configuration)\n301 | - Systems Engineers (local weight tuning & pipeline performance)\n302 | - Security Compliance Auditor (zero-retention validation logging)\n303 | \n304 | SECTION VII: GOVERNANCE APPROACH\n305 | GFF enforces a \"Zero Trust, Zero Retention\" sovereign AI governance framework. Prompt-history is instantly zeroed out post-execution, and telemetry logs are recorded to a read-only audit ledger.\n306 | \n307 | SECTION VIII: SUCCESS MEASURES\n308 | - Latency: Sub-150ms dynamic cognitive decision loops.\n309 | - IP Safety: Absolute zero external IP leaks or SaaS memory retention logs.\n310 | - OpEx Reclamation: 30%+ reclaimed external SaaS token and licensing expenses.\n311 | - Telemetry Auditing: 100% logging coverage verified by the secure audit ledger.\n312 | \n313 | SECTION IX: ASSUMPTIONS\n314 | - Read-only database access is granted via VPC boundaries within 7 business days.\n315 | - Stakeholders listed (${data.stakeholdersLabel}) participate in weekly 15-minute syncs.\n316 | \n317 | SECTION X: RISKS & MITIGATIONS\n318 | - Risk: Legacy silo schema complexity. Mitigation: GFF OmniMesh builds semantic indices without altering original sources.\n319 | - Risk: Isolated hardware lead-times. Mitigation: Prototype on staging enclaves.\n320 | \n321 | SECTION XI: NEXT STEPS\n322 | 1. Complete digital sign-off.\n323 | 2. VPC configurations & discovery call.\n324 | 3. Mobilize co-innovation squad (${data.engagementPathObj.squad}) in 7 days.\n325 | `;\n326 |     navigator.clipboard.writeText(outlineText);\n327 |     setCopied(true);\n328 |     setTimeout(() => setCopied(false), 2000);\n329 |   };\n330 | \n331 |   const generateProposalData = () => {\n332 |     const org = inputs.companyName.trim() || \"Enterprise Client\";\n333 |     const indObj = INDUSTRIES.find((i) => i.id === inputs.industry) || INDUSTRIES[0];\n334 |     const sizeObj = COMPANY_SIZES.find((s) => s.id === inputs.companySize) || COMPANY_SIZES[2];\n335 |     const pathObj = ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find((p) => p.id === inputs.preferredEngagementPath) || ENGAGEMENT_PATHS[1];\n336 |     const timelineObj = TIMELINES.find((t) => t.id === inputs.targetTimeline) || TIMELINES[1];\n337 |     const budgetObj = BUDGET_RANGES.find((b) => b.id === inputs.budgetRange) || BUDGET_RANGES[1];\n338 | \n339 |     const challengeLabel = inputs.primaryChallenge === \"other\" && inputs.customChallenge.trim()\n340 |       ? inputs.customChallenge.trim()\n341 |       : (CHALLENGES.find((c) => c.id === inputs.primaryChallenge)?.label || \"Sovereign Integration\");\n342 | \n343 |     const geographyLabel = inputs.geography.trim() || \"Global Private VPC Network Perimeter\";\n344 |     const stakeholdersLabel = inputs.stakeholders.trim() || \"Chief Technology Officer, Compliance Committee\";\n345 | \n346 |     const selectedOutcomeLabels = inputs.priorityOutcomes.map(\n347 |       (out) => OUTCOMES.find((o) => o.id === out)?.label || out\n348 |     );\n349 | \n350 |     let calculatedWeeks = timelineObj.weeks;\n351 |     if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"garage\") calculatedWeeks = 4;\n352 |     else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"operate\") calculatedWeeks = 52;\n353 |     else {\n354 |       if (inputs.companySize === \"small\") calculatedWeeks = Math.max(4, calculatedWeeks - 4);\n355 |       else if (inputs.companySize === \"global-conglomerate\") calculatedWeeks = calculatedWeeks + 4;\n356 |     }\n357 | \n358 |     const p1 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.15));\n359 |     const p2 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.30));\n360 |     const p3 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.40));\n361 |     const p4 = Math.max(1, calculatedWeeks - (p1 + p2 + p3));\n362 | \n363 |     let deliverables: string[] = [];\n364 |     if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"garage\") {\n365 |       deliverables = [\n366 |         \"Interactive high-velocity client sandbox prototype\",\n367 |         \"Strategic SOW architecture topology outline schema\",\n368 |         \"Initial data pipeline schema risk audit assessment\",\n369 |         \"Targeted performance benchmarking telemetry sheet\"\n370 |       ];\n371 |     } else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"foundry\") {\n372 |       deliverables = [\n373 |         \"Fully provisioned, isolated single-tenant private VPC perimeter\",\n374 |         \"Tailored multi-agent consensus network and workflow configurations\",\n375 |         \"Hardened OmniMesh read-only legacy data connector pipelines\",\n376 |         \"Enterprise-wide compliance audit ledger logging software\"\n377 |       ];\n378 |     } else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"factory\") {\n379 |       deliverables = [\n380 |         \"Industrial-scale federated data mesh network connectors\",\n381 |         \"Autonomous auto-scaling cross-department agent fleet systems\",\n382 |         \"Highly integrated compliance watchdog and safety enforcer software\",\n383 |         \"Sovereign multi-region VPC peering configurations\"\n384 |       ];\n385 |     } else {\n386 |       deliverables = [\n387 |         \"Active monitoring uptime and model performance telemetry panels\",\n388 |         \"Guaranteed 99.9% operational performance SLA monitoring setup\",\n389 |         \"Proactive scheduled compliance and data policy updates\",\n390 |         \"Weekly technical optimization analysis reports and audit files\"\n391 |       ];\n392 |     }\n393 | \n394 |     return {\n395 |       org,\n396 |       industryLabel: indObj.label,\n397 |       industryDesc: indObj.desc,\n398 |       industryIcon: indObj.icon,\n399 |       companySizeLabel: sizeObj.label,\n400 |       companySizeDesc: sizeObj.desc,\n401 |       companySizeRange: sizeObj.range,\n402 |       challengeLabel,\n403 |       timelineLabel: timelineObj.label,\n404 |       weeks: calculatedWeeks,\n405 |       engagementPathObj: pathObj,\n406 |       budgetLabel: inputs.budgetRange ? budgetObj.label : \"Tailored Strategic Budget\",\n407 |       geographyLabel,\n408 |       stakeholdersLabel,\n409 |       selectedOutcomeLabels,\n410 |       deliverables,\n411 |       p1, p2, p3, p4\n412 |     };\n413 |   };\n414 | \n415 |   const pData = generateProposalData();\n416 | \n417 |   const renderTopologyDiagram = (path: \"garage\" | \"foundry\" | \"factory\" | \"operate\") => {\n418 |     return (\n419 |       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl bg-[#030305] border border-white/5 font-mono text-[9px] text-white/50 space-y-3\">\n420 |         <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[7px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n421 |           <span>DEPLOYMENT TOPOLOGY MAP</span>\n422 |           <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">{path.toUpperCase()}_ACTIVE_NODE</span>\n423 |         </d