tabase migrations and system modifications for PII leaks, storage location violations, and rule breaches.\",\n366 |     recommendedIndustry: \"Government & Sovereign\",\n367 |     relatedPlatform: \"Assessment Mesh / Auditor\",\n368 |     agentType: \"Guardrail / Audit\",\n369 |     status: \"Enclave Verified\",\n370 |     securityRating: \"Military-Grade Secure\",\n371 |     metrics: {\n372 |       cpu: \"16-Core vCPU\",\n373 |       memory: \"64GB Isolated\",\n374 |       isolation: \"AMD SEV-SNP\",\n375 |       compliance: \"GDPR / HIPAA / FedRAMP\"\n376 |     },\n377 |     ingressLabel: \"Database Config & Commits\",\n378 |     egressLabel: \"Compliance Block / Approval\",\n379 |     steps: [\n380 |       {\n381 |         title: \"Boundary Scanning\",\n382 |         description: \"Scans new code commits, schema files, and storage bucket descriptors for geopolitical regulatory alignment.\",\n383 |         role: \"Sovereign Boundary Agent\"\n384 |       },\n385 |       {\n386 |         title: \"PII Deep Scanning\",\n387 |         description: \"Analyzes system outputs, log files, and API structures for unmasked identity attributes.\",\n388 |         role: \"PII Pattern Agent\"\n389 |       },\n390 |       {\n391 |         title: \"Sovereign Enclave Validation\",\n392 |         description: \"Verifies that processing nodes remain fully inside localized geo-redundant boundaries.\",\n393 |         role: \"Hardware Enclave Validator\"\n394 |       },\n395 |       {\n396 |         title: \"Automated Pipeline Interlock\",\n397 |         description: \"Forces automated rollback locks on compliance breaches and reports telemetry directly to the CISO dashboard.\",\n398 |         role: \"Lockout Protocol Agent\"\n399 |       }\n400 |     ],\n401 |     challenge: \"Enterprise data pipelines crossing international borders face immediate fines if they transmit sensitive customer records outside sovereign borders. Compliance officers cannot inspect millions of high-velocity payload streams manually.\",\n402 |     interpretation: \"Inspects incoming and outgoing streaming data payloads at the API Gateway level. Detects and blocks PII, health information (PHI), or localized data transgressions in real time.\",\n403 |     knowledgeNeeded: [\n404 |       \"EU GDPR directives handbook\",\n405 |       \"CCPA regulatory frameworks\",\n406 |       \"HIPAA Protected Health Information (PHI) identifiers catalog\",\n407 |       \"Enterprise custom localized data categorization schema\"\n408 |     ],\n409 |     humanApproval: \"Data Protection Officer (DPO) is alerted to review blocked payloads and decide whether to whitelist specific encrypted tokens.\",\n410 |     governanceCheck: \"Zero-Trust gateway prevents egress of non-anonymized data; automated audit-trail hash is written to the immutable compliance ledger.\",\n411 |     outputPreview: \"{\\n  \\\"gateway_session\\\": \\\"GW-9921-X\\\",\\n  \\\"packets_inspected\\\": \\\"41,209\\\",\\n  \\\"violations_detected\\\": \\\"1 (PII/Social Security Number detected in Outbound Payload #882)\\\",\\n  \\\"action_taken\\\": \\\"PAYLOAD_MUTED_AND_REDACTED\\\",\\n  \\\"compliance_status\\\": \\\"SECURED\\\"\\n}\",\n412 |     logs: [\n413 |       { timeOffset: 0.2, type: \"system\", text: \"Listening on CI/CD production deployment pipeline webhook...\" },\n414 |       { timeOffset: 0.8, type: \"info\", text: \"Analyzing pending database migration script (Commit: #10941).\" },\n415 |       { timeOffset: 1.5, type: \"agent\", text: \"[BoundaryAgent] Scanning region. Destination: Frankfurt-Zone-1. Status: Sovereign Compliant.\" },\n416 |       { timeOffset: 2.2, type: \"agent\", text: \"[PIIAgent] Parsing table structure 'UserBillingDetails'...\" },\n417 |       { timeOffset: 2.9, type: \"warning\", text: \"[PIIAgent] Found unencrypted field 'TaxID'. Violation of GDPR Article 32: Privacy by Design.\" },\n418 |       { timeOffset: 3.6, type: \"agent\", text: \"[LockoutAgent] INTERLOCK ENGAGED: Halting build deployment. Rejecting code promotion.\" },\n419 |       { timeOffset: 4.3, type: \"success\", text: \"CISO notified. Rollback completed successfully inside sandbox.\" }\n420 |     ]\n421 |   },\n422 |   {\n423 |     id: \"customer-experience\",\n424 |     name: \"Sovereign Support & Resolution Agent\",\n425 |     category: \"Customer Experience Agent\",\n426 |     purpose: \"Resolves billing inquiries, diagnostic anomalies, and service adjustments within zero-trust sandboxed limits.\",\n427 |     recommendedIndustry: \"Telecom\",\n428 |     relatedPlatform: \"TelecomVerse\",\n429 |     agentType: \"Real-time / Interactive\",\n430 |     status: \"Ready for Simulation\",\n431 |     securityRating: \"Hardened Gateway\",\n432 |     metrics: {\n433 |       cpu: \"4-Core vCPU\",\n434 |       memory: \"16GB Secure\",\n435 |       isolation: \"Intel SGX Enclave\",\n436 |       compliance: \"TCPA / HIPAA Compliant\"\n437 |     },\n438 |     ingressLabel: \"User Support Chat Thread\",\n439 |     egressLabel: \"Billing Credit & SMS Alert\",\n440 |     steps: [\n441 |       {\n442 |         title: \"Intent Parsing & Verification\",\n443 |         description: \"Resolves primary customer request topic while validating user secure-token claims.\",\n444 |         role: \"Customer Intent Classifier\"\n445 |       },\n446 |       {\n447 |         title: \"Database Telemetry Query\",\n448 |         description: \"Retrieves network registers, historical invoices, and billing traces inside secured read-only memory.\",\n449 |         role: \"Billing Database Connector\"\n450 |       },\n451 |       {\n452 |         title: \"Resolution Strategy Engine\",\n453 |         description: \"Computes loyalty credits or service tier modifications based on enterprise policy guidelines.\",\n454 |         role: \"Policy Execution Agent\"\n455 |       },\n456 |       {\n457 |         title: \"Secured Transaction Run\",\n458 |         description: \"Fires secure webhooks to credit billing profiles and sends cryptographically verified notifications.\",\n459 |         role: \"Transaction Runner Agent\"\n460 |       }\n461 |     ],\n462 |     challenge: \"Large-scale customer support centers suffer from slow resolution times and high operational costs, yet generic AI chatbots frustrate high-net-worth customers by giving repetitive, unhelpful, and generic answers.\",\n463 |     interpretation: \"Analyzes user history and emotional sentiment. Cross-references internal knowledge bases, and formulates precise, highly contextual, empathetic resolutions.\",\n464 |     knowledgeNeeded: [\n465 |       \"Customer CRM transaction records\",\n466 |       \"Internal product resolution logs\",\n467 |       \"Live courier and shipping status APIs\",\n468 |       \"Tone of Voice & Sentiment Guardrails\"\n469 |     ],\n470 |     humanApproval: \"Support Supervisor reviews and edits responses for ultra-high-priority VIP clients before sending the final email or message.\",\n471 |     governanceCheck: \"Safety filter blocks toxic language, and prevents the agent from promising refunds or credits beyond pre-approved thresholds.\",\n472 |     outputPreview: \"{\\n  \\\"client_tier\\\": \\\"VIP_PLATINUM\\\",\\n  \\\"sentiment\\\": \\\"FRUSTRATED\\\",\\n  \\\"detected_issue\\\": \\\"Delayed delivery of custom industrial server rack\\\",\\n  \\\"proposed_solution\\\": \\\"Express courier redirection + $200 service credit\\\",\\n  \\\"response_draft\\\": \\\"Dear Mr. Vance, we sincerely apologize for the delay. We have upgraded your shipping to overnight express...\\\"\\n}\",\n473 |     logs: [\n474 |       { timeOffset: 0.1, type: \"system\", text: \"Initializing Customer Support Enclave inside isolated sandbox host...\" },\n475 |       { timeOffset: 0.8, type: \"info\", text: \"Successfully linked with Salesforce CRM & DHL Logistics API connectors.\" },\n476 |       { timeOffset: 1.5, type: \"agent\", text: \"[SentimentClassifier] Ticket ID #9921 analyzed. Customer emotional index: FRUSTR