how to extract the links to \"relevant Capabilities and Platforms\", which I am now calling out as: `/capabilities/labs`, `/capabilities/universities`, `/capabilities/knowledge-graph`, `/capabilities/twins`, `/capabilities/agents`, `/capabilities/operations`, `/capabilities/governance`, `/capabilities/managed-services`, `/capabilities/data`, and `/capabilities/engineering`. I'm starting from the available folder structure to make sure I find the right links!\n\n\n"}}
